### Decision: Session summary: Fixed two bugs in onboarding flow. (1) Hydration mismatch — OnboardingProvider was 

**Date:** 2026-02-19
**Context:** Session summary: Fixed two bugs in onboarding flow
**Decision:** Session summary: Fixed two bugs in onboarding flow. (1) Hydration mismatch — OnboardingProvider was reading localStorage in useState initializers causing server/client mismatch. Fixed by deferring all localStorage reads to useEffect with isLoading state. (2) Data leaking between users — localStorage key was global, not per-user. Fixed by adding userId to stored data and validating on load, clearing stale data on mismatch. Also fixed middleware (ASP-B-4) to check subscription_id/is_vip before allowing dashboard access, preventing users from bypassing payment via browser back button.
**Reasoning:** 

